    <p class="lede">Mainstream GE 30" single and double built-in wall ovens — our techs service GE wall ovens across LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. Mainstream GE is the base mass-market tier within GE Appliances' wall oven hierarchy — below GE Profile (feature-focused premium), GE Café (style-first premium), and GE Monogram (ultra-luxury). Haier-owned GE Appliances since 2016, Louisville Kentucky US distribution supports reliable parts supply for both current and older GE wall oven installs across the LA metro area. $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
