      <div class="model-card"><h3>GE 30" double built-in wall oven</h3><p>Stacked dual-cavity. Upper + lower independent elements + sensors, shared primary control.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Pre-2016 GE wall ovens (pre-Haier ownership)</h3><p>Widely installed across LA. Parts reliably available through Louisville KY distribution; some specialty pre-2010 parts longer lead.</p></div>
